  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.0.0-alpha02\" data-text=\"Version 1.0.0-alpha02\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.0.0-alpha02</h3>\n<p>December 3, 2018</p>\n<p><strong>API changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added a note that <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">getLifecycle()</code> should not be overridden and will be made\n<code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">final</code> in a future release. Please <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/new?component=197448\">file a feature\nrequest</a> if you\nare currently overriding this method. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/platform/frameworks/support/+/815834\">aosp/815834</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
